<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Nouveau message de contact</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #1f2937; background: #f9fafb; margin: 0; padding: 24px;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
        <tr>
            <td style="background: #111827; padding: 24px; color: #ffffff;">
                <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase;">Hollywood Paris</h1>
                <p style="margin: 4px 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #d1d5db;">Nouveau message via le formulaire de contact</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 24px;">
                <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Expéditeur</p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 16px;"><a href="mailto:{{ senderEmail }}" style="color: #111827;">{{ senderEmail }}</a></p>

                <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Sujet</p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;">{{ subject }}</p>

                <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Message</p>
                <div style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: pre-wrap; padding: 16px; background: #f9fafb; border-left: 3px solid #111827; border-radius: 4px;">{{ message }}</div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 16px 24px; background: #f9fafb; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280;">
                Répondez directement à cet email pour contacter l'expéditeur.
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
